<HEADLINE> Hang Seng China Enterprises Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Hang Seng China Enterprises
Index today fell 16.57 points to close at 778.52.
</P>
