The Index, introduced in August 1995, tracks the overall
performance of China's 32 state enterprises listed on the Hong
Kong Stock Exchange.
</P>
<P>
Today's Hang Seng MidCap 50 Index dropped 4.56 points from the
previous session to close at 1,307.91.
