<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice Premier Qian
Qichen said here today that China, as a permanent member of the UN
Security Council and a major Asia-Pacific country, attaches great
importance to and works unswervingly for peace and prosperity in
the Asia-Pacific region.
</P>
<P>
Qian, who is also China's foreign minister, made the remarks at
a business forum titled "A Private Sector Salute to ASEAN" this
