reduction, namely, on the basis of the cut by one million troops
in the 1980s, an additional 500,000 troops will be cut in the next
three years.
</P>
<P>
China's relations with Russia, the United States, Japan and
other countries have made positive progress through recent
meetings of state and government leaders.
</P>
<P>
"China will continue to seek settlement of disputes with its
neighbors through friendly consultation and negotiation, while
setting store by maintaining the larger interests of peace and
security," Qian said.
</P>
<P>
He pointed out, "A prosperous and progressing china needs a
peaceful, stable and prosperous East Asia. We will surely make
our due contribution to peace, stability and prosperity of East
Asia." 
