<HEADLINE> Harbin Wins China's Ice Hockey League </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Harbin beat Qiqihar 4-2 in the
final to become China's National Ice Hockey League champion here
Sunday night.
</P>
