Zhao Liang scored 30 seconds and 1:30 into the opening period
to put Harbin ahead 2-0.
</P>
<P>
Qiqihar, who defeated Harbin three times in their previous four
encounters in the round-robin preliminaries, pulled one back near
the end of the first period.
</P>
