period, while Harbin strengthened the lead by adding one in each
of the second and third periods.
</P>
<P>
In the play-off for the third place, Jiamusi defeated Jilin 5-4
by scoring in the sudden-death overtime after the two sides tied
4-4 (1-3; 1-1; 2-0) after 60 minutes.
</P>
<P>
Guo Xiaowu scored the "golden goal" 1:05 into the overtime.
</P>
<P>
The league only have four teams, which all come from the three
northeastern provinces of Heilongjiang, Jilin and Liaoning.
