<HEADLINE> Australia Holds Brazil to 0-0 Draw </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT, December 14 (Xinhua) -- Australia held world champion
Brazil to a love-all draw in their Confederations' Cup group A
soccer match in Riyadh on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Australian defenders and goalkeeper Mark Bosnich proved the
heroes against the star-studded Brazilian team.
</P>
<P>
